SMPL workstations should have verbose mode set in nvram boot-args on startup:

To permanently start up in verbose mode:  sudo nvram boot-args="-v"
To disable all nvram boot-args:  sudo nvram boot-args=
To check nvram settings:  nvram -p 

----

Disable per-session history file in Mojave:  touch ~/.bash_sessions_disable .

----

defaults write com.apple.finder _FXShowPosixPathInTitle -bool false; killall Finder

